import React from 'react' import { difficultyLevels, durationLevels } from './ActivitiesLevels' import style from './ActivityCard.module.css' import difficultyIco from '../icons/equalizer_black_24dp.svg' import durationIco from '../icons/date_range_black_24dp.svg' import seasonIco from '../icons/timelapse_black_24dp.svg' export default function ActivityCard({ name, difficulty, duration, season }) { return (

{name}

Difficulty {difficultyLevels[difficulty - 1]}
Duration {durationLevels[duration - 1]}
Season {season}
) }
